## Summary
This documentation explains the row limits and sorting logic in Data Tables charts, detailing how Amplitude Analytics displays results (100-500 rows for top-level group-bys), applies sorting only to displayed results, and enforces different export limits based on metric types (10,000 for event segmentation, 300 for funnels, 100 for sessions, and 20 for attribution metrics).

